 Western culture.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aPhilosophy, Chinese. 0aThought and thinking. 7aPHILOSOPHY / History & Surveys / General.2bisacsh1 aGladding, Jody.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015z978311067250340uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030021360740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300213607423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300213607/original  a978-3-11-067250-3  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015c2014d2015  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles